	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />This is related to my comment in the PPU Quirk topic.  What is a good set of combinations to test your homebrew on?  Do people just test against any old US NES or NOAC clones?  I think I read licensed developers needed to test against at least 3 revisions of NES boards.  What do people consider a reasonable set of combinations to test against?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
